Abraham Lincoln Mills Life Mask

Files:
    lincoln_life_mask.obj  — mesh (150K triangles, 15 MB, OBJ format)
    lincoln_life_mask.mtl  — material definition
    lincoln_life_mask_diffuse.jpg
    lincoln_life_mask_normals.jpg
